<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197608>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 18. Casuarinicola nigrimaculatus sp. nov. (12), habitus, female (dorsal aspect); (13), habitus, male (dorsal aspect); (14), habitus female (lateral aspect); (15), habitus male (lateral aspect); (16), fore wing, female; (17), fore wing, male; (18), head (dorsal aspect). Scale = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197610>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 29. Casuarinicola nigrimaculatus sp. nov. and C. mucronalatus, sp. nov. Casuarinicola nigrimaculatus, sp. nov. (24), male terminalia (lateral aspect); (25), paramere (inner face, lateral aspect); (26), female terminalia, (lateral aspect); Casuarinicola mucronalatus sp. nov. (27), male terminalia (lateral aspect); (28), paramere (inner face, lateral aspect); (29), female terminalia, (lateral aspect: note alignment of circumanal pore ring is an artefact). Scale = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197610/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197614>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 – 51. Distribution for Australian species of Casuarinicola gen. nov.: (50),, Casuarinicola australis sp. nov.; (51),, C. nigrimaculatus sp. nov.;, C. mucronalatus sp. nov.;, C. warrigalensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

